### Usage Metering properties ###

-Dmetering.logger.pattern=/opt/ibm/wlp/usr/servers/defaultServer/apps/decisioncenter.war/assets/metering.log
-Dmetering.logger.limit=50000000
-Dmetering.logger.count=50
-Dmetering.logger.force.logging=true
-Dcom.ibm.rules.metering.log.usages=true
-Dcom.ibm.rules.metering.enable=true
